Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: ε
    2        | program automation

    3 $@1: ε

    4 automation: CREATE STRING $@1 COLON fields

    5 fields: ε
    6       | fields field

    7 field: ID STRING
    8      | ID NUMBER
    9      | DESCRIPTION STRING
   10      | MODE IDENTIFIER
   11      | LISTEN LBRACKET listen_items RBRACKET
   12      | WHEN LBRACKET condition_items RBRACKET
   13      | DO LBRACKET action_items RBRACKET

   14 listen_items: listen_item
   15             | listen_items COMMA listen_item

   16 listen_item: LPAREN attr_list RPAREN

   17 condition_items: condition_item
   18                | condition_items COMMA condition_item

   19 condition_item: LPAREN attr_list RPAREN

   20 attr_list: ε
   21          | attr
   22          | attr_list attr

   23 attr: DEVICE_ID IDENTIFIER
   24     | ENTITY_ID IDENTIFIER
   25     | STATEKW IS IDENTIFIER
   26     | TIMEKW AFTER TIME_LITERAL
   27     | TIMEKW BEFORE TIME_LITERAL
   28     | STATEKW CHANGES TO IDENTIFIER
   29     | IDENTIFIER IS IDENTIFIER
   30     | IDENTIFIER IDENTIFIER
   31     | IDENTIFIER LBRACKET id_list RBRACKET
   32     | CHANGES TO IDENTIFIER
   33     | WITH IDENTIFIER LBRACKET id_list RBRACKET

   34 id_list: IDENTIFIER
   35        | IDENTIFIER COMMA id_list

   36 action_items: action_item
   37             | action_item COMMA action_items

   38 action_item: LPAREN action_body RPAREN

   39 action_body: IF condition_group action_block else_part
   40            | simple_action

   41 condition_group: LBRACKET condition_items RBRACKET
   42                | LPAREN attr_list RPAREN

   43 action_block: ε
   44             | simple_action
   45             | action_block simple_action

   46 else_part: ELSE IF condition_group action_block else_part
   47          | ELSE action_block
   48          | ε

   49 simple_action: DELAY DURATION_LITERAL
   50              | AUTOMATION TRIGGERKW attr_list
   51              | IDENTIFIER IDENTIFIER attr_list


